00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.950 align:middle line:84%
And I would say that the
last three years of my life

00:01:01.950 --> 00:01:06.450 align:middle line:84%
have been an exceptional
journey for me.

00:01:06.450 --> 00:01:09.600 align:middle line:84%
It's been like being in the
