00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:09.090 align:middle line:84%
So one thing that happened
to me in the first class

00:20:09.090 --> 00:20:12.180 align:middle line:84%
was, we do what's called an open
search inward where you go down

00:20:12.180 --> 00:20:15.300 align:middle line:84%
the timeline of your own soul
and you see why you're here,

00:20:15.300 --> 00:20:16.120 align:middle line:90%
among other things.

00:20:16.120 --> 00:20:18.370 align:middle line:90%
And that a big thing for me.

00:20:18.370 --> 00:20:20.070 align:middle line:84%
I should tell you
that before this,

00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:23.140 align:middle line:84%
I really didn't talk much for
the first 25 years of my life.

00:20:23.140 --> 00:20:26.520 align:middle line:84%
And it was a big challenge
for me to connect to people.

00:20:26.520 --> 00:20:30.060 align:middle line:84%
And now, here I am
a year later back

00:20:30.060 --> 00:20:33.900 align:middle line:84%
on the Omega Campus with David
helping people in that way.

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:36.240 align:middle line:84%
And it's a challenge
for me every time I

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:38.400 align:middle line:84%
get up in front of
the room, but it's

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:41.040 align:middle line:84%
humbling to see what people
are willing to go through.

00:20:41.040 --> 00:20:45.270 align:middle line:84%
So now, with the classes,
I help find, select,

00:20:45.270 --> 00:20:50.580 align:middle line:84%
and develop the videos and
the audiovisual portion

00:20:50.580 --> 00:20:53.100 align:middle line:84%
of the class so
it becomes as much

00:20:53.100 --> 00:20:55.120 align:middle line:84%
of a rich experience
for them as possible.

00:20:55.120 --> 00:20:59.640 align:middle line:84%
So when they go somewhere
distant in time and space,

00:20:59.640 --> 00:21:01.140 align:middle line:84%
we can give them
as much information

00:21:01.140 --> 00:21:06.000 align:middle line:84%
as possible for where they've
been, and justification to it,

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:09.840 align:middle line:84%
for having experiencing
what they were experiencing.

00:21:09.840 --> 00:21:12.330 align:middle line:84%
Also I lead moving
meditation in the mornings

00:21:12.330 --> 00:21:16.620 align:middle line:84%
and some small yoga
practice, gentle yoga,

00:21:16.620 --> 00:21:18.060 align:middle line:90%
depending on where they are.

00:21:18.060 --> 00:21:21.240 align:middle line:84%
So it's a constant challenge
for me personally, day to day,

00:21:21.240 --> 00:21:23.850 align:middle line:84%
because, here I am, someone
who, their entire life,

00:21:23.850 --> 00:21:30.120 align:middle line:84%
was internal and introverted
having to express and open

00:21:30.120 --> 00:21:33.330 align:middle line:84%
up people physically,
when I, for 25 years,

00:21:33.330 --> 00:21:36.960 align:middle line:84%
was very uncomfortable
with physical contact.

00:21:36.960 --> 00:21:40.090 align:middle line:84%
And it's just to be with them
and help them experience,

00:21:40.090 --> 00:21:43.200 align:middle line:84%
be open to and accept who they
are, no matter what that is,

00:21:43.200 --> 00:21:45.737 align:middle line:84%
and to understand that
they are part of a family

00:21:45.737 --> 00:21:47.070 align:middle line:90%
when they come to these classes.

00:21:47.070 --> 00:21:48.872 align:middle line:90%
And I protect them fiercely.

00:21:48.872 --> 00:21:51.420 align:middle line:84%
And these people are
very important to me.

00:21:51.420 --> 00:21:54.270 align:middle line:84%
And anyone that comes in
is treated the same way.

00:21:54.270 --> 00:21:56.340 align:middle line:90%
I love them very much.

00:21:56.340 --> 00:21:58.500 align:middle line:84%
I had been asking
myself for years,

00:21:58.500 --> 00:22:03.120 align:middle line:84%
and that I wanted an honest open
direct experience with life,

00:22:03.120 --> 00:22:06.630 align:middle line:84%
but what I found was that I
needed to really challenge

00:22:06.630 --> 00:22:09.120 align:middle line:84%
myself and share what
I'd been through,

00:22:09.120 --> 00:22:12.630 align:middle line:84%
because I had put myself through
personal hells for a few years

00:22:12.630 --> 00:22:13.560 align:middle line:90%
before that.

00:22:13.560 --> 00:22:19.960 align:middle line:84%
I had to go through leaving
the one woman who, to this day,

00:22:19.960 --> 00:22:22.650 align:middle line:84%
I still think about
to be here now,

00:22:22.650 --> 00:22:24.150 align:middle line:84%
and to be able to
have experienced

00:22:24.150 --> 00:22:29.670 align:middle line:84%
what I did since that day to
allow myself to share this

00:22:29.670 --> 00:22:31.800 align:middle line:84%
with the students in class,
and with people I meet,

00:22:31.800 --> 00:22:34.260 align:middle line:84%
and whoever is open
to it, to allow

00:22:34.260 --> 00:22:38.820 align:middle line:84%
them to be open to their
version of that story.

00:22:38.820 --> 00:22:42.620 align:middle line:90%
Because it has helped, I think.

00:22:42.620 --> 00:22:44.580 align:middle line:84%
People have thanked me
for when I tell them

00:22:44.580 --> 00:22:47.550 align:middle line:84%
about this or about
other things like it,

00:22:47.550 --> 00:22:50.700 align:middle line:84%
because there have
been quite a few.

00:22:50.700 --> 00:22:52.800 align:middle line:84%
But that, I think that was
the most painful thing,

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:57.030 align:middle line:84%
because anytime I'm alone and
walking the street or even

00:22:57.030 --> 00:23:00.920 align:middle line:84%
with someone, I kind of hope
to see her turn the corner.

00:23:00.920 --> 00:23:04.600 align:middle line:84%
Every day, I think
of her every day.

00:23:04.600 --> 00:23:07.650 align:middle line:84%
But I still know the
decision was right,

00:23:07.650 --> 00:23:12.390 align:middle line:84%
because what I'm doing now is
important on a scale that's

00:23:12.390 --> 00:23:13.830 align:middle line:90%
beyond me.

00:23:13.830 --> 00:23:16.180 align:middle line:84%
And I know that's
why I'm really here.

